{
  "stem": "26609.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went-- I can't read a lot-- not a lot, not a bit about in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is Warszawa, there is Lodz, there is Lublin that I read about, but not about the Lwow march.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the hospital, [INAUDIBLE] with the patients alive, was set on fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I finished nursing, you know, with the three years additional with nursing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I finished right to '37, to my marriage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then '39, my daughter was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know pregnancy takes nine months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's nearly another years, so I didn't have much time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nor-- during pregnancy, I didn't work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after, we had the Soviets, '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was actually born into the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Soviets came, and I-- I couldn't work in my profession.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't work as a-- but with the Soviets, the child was in a-- how did they call it?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For not a full time, from-- to say from 9:00 to 3:00.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know what is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like here, they have the child care.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Daycare.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was different there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the polytechnic was-- that's where my brother studied-- my husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Polytechnic was on the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the street, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was converted during the Russian-- when the Russians-- Soviets were-- in a month, it was converted to a laboratorium, lab, you know, laboratory-- a medical laboratory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they assigned me there to work in the laboratory instead of hospitals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't have enough people, so--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was after the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was when the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians were from-- because first, we had the Germans, and they changed positions, since the Russians-- and-- and they-- pushed them out.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
